title: DE161OTRSSS Microwave Oven Built-in 1000-Watts with 10 Power Levels Pre Settings and Express, Sensor and Speed Cooking and Silent Mode with Glass Turntable, 1.6 cu.ft, Metallic
description: Our DUURA Elite® Over-the-Range Microwave Oven makes preparing multiple dishes effortless with its 1.6 cu. ft. capacity, accommodating your different cooking needs. The touchscreen control panel provides a seamless, integrated look, ensuring all design elements will match in your kitchen. Sensor cook technology automatically adjusts your cooking time for optimal results. Additionally, the grey interior provides a durable and easy-to-clean surface, making everyday maintenance simple.
